Package it.polimi.ingsw.am37.model

Class Island

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.am37.model.UpdatableObject
it.polimi.ingsw.am37.model.Island
public class Island extends UpdatableObject
At the beginning of the game there are twelve islands, they can have students on them and tower which represents that a player is controlling them. Islands can be united and once this happens can't be reversed
